{{nihongo|Nekama|ネカマ|}} is a [[Japanese language|Japanese]] term used to describe a kind of [[internet sock puppet]] used on dating and personal sites. The word is a [[Japanese abbreviated and contracted words|combination]] of ''netto'' (inter'''net'''), and ''[[okama]]'' drag artist, and means a man who posts a personal advert using a female identity. ''Nekama'' range from the blatantly obvious, for example using a photo scanned from a girlie magazine and blatantly sexually provocative message, to the subtle and hard to spot. There are many Japanese web sites dealing with ''nekama'' and how to spot them.

